{"comments":"Shape operator property records.\n\nEach shape operator (TrimPaths, PuckerBloat, WigglePaths, etc.) needs\nactual data — not just an enum tag, but the complete set of bounded\nproperties that define its behavior.\n\n## Architecture\n\nShape operators transform paths. Each operator has:\n- A discriminator (ShapeContentType from Shapes.purs)\n- Property records with bounded values\n- Default constructors\n\nAll values are bounded to ensure deterministic behavior at swarm scale.\n\n## Operator Categories\n\n- **Path Modifiers**: TrimPaths, OffsetPaths, RoundedCorners\n- **Distortions**: PuckerBloat, ZigZag, Twist, WigglePaths\n- **Duplication**: Repeater\n- **Combination**: MergePaths\n- **Transform**: ShapeTransform\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"TrimPaths operator properties.\n\nTrims the visible portion of a path, creating stroke-draw effects.\n- start: Where path begins (0-100%)\n- end: Where path ends (0-100%)\n- offset: Rotates the trim point around the path\n- mode: Whether to trim all paths together or individually\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["start",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Motion","Shapes","Operators"],"Percent"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["end",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Motion","Shapes","Operators"],"Percent"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["offset",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Motion","Shapes","Operators"],"Degrees"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["mode",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Motion","Shapes"],"TrimMode"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[246,4],"name":"../../hyd